text.tspan: Big Band, or Ben, was, in a past life, a policeman, until
his coworkers took him to a dark alley and beat him
senseless. He was presumed dead, with a statement being
released detailing that he overdosed on weed. A few days
later, his comatose body was found by the MCS. They
lobotomised him and rebuilt his battered body, turning him
Now this was quite a humorous little brouhaha amongst
the MCS higher ups, but it dawned upon them that they
could make Big Bank off of this…
Now he’s a member of Musteezer, the totally legit band,
in which he plays the sax, trumpets, trombones, rhythm
section- okay yeah he pretty much does everything. So that’s
his life now! Nope, never experienced racism a day in his life!
